long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly export Behance hire listings from the hire search page to XLS/CSV file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Open an Behance hire listing page.
2️⃣ Click open our extension, then click the Export button.
3️⃣ Done! Sit back and just wait a moment, let our extension handle the rest.

🔥 Key Features:
1️⃣ Run in the background without waiting for finish.
2️⃣ Export on multiple hire listing pages simultaneous.
3️⃣ Export listing data for current search page to a xls/csv file, data include: User Id, Allows Contact From Anyone, Availability Timeline, Currency, Hiring Timeline, Is Available Freelance, Is Available FullTime, Is Looking For Remote, Country, UserName, User Image Url, Is Featured Freelancer, Location, Project Info, Appreciations, Followers, Views, User Url, Search Url.

🎯 Targeted Users: business owners, data analysts, and competitor researchers alike.

💡 Benefit from our dedicated support team! We're here to assist you at every step and provide prompt, knowledgeable help.

💪 Take control of your business data management and make informed decisions with Behance  Hire Exporter today!

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Behance ❗️🔒
